{"type": "article", "id": 28852, "title": "金属搁板", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-29T06:59:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121512boi5EawkrTAGuYlx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你有用搁板收纳小物的习惯，不妨看看英国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.kukkastudio.co.uk/\">kukka</a> 推出的这套 Ridges 金属搁板。每一块都经过激光切割并且折叠成了简单的几何形状，搭配上鲜亮的颜色就好像是在墙上建立了一个特别的小空间。你可以通过三角形的缺口摆上小物，或者利用金属磁性悬挂一些装饰品。这是它的<a href=\"http://kukka.co.uk/collections/home/products/ridges\">购买链接</a>，售价为 280 英镑，每一块搁板还附带一个浅盘。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121510bxB9ZvVrLwh8nAci.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215118gceKAIsBCzOb0hw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121511qZEpvMlcVWSsyhxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121512CHZF4T9R6LU03kmY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}